### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### English inventory summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/summary?lang=en

### Swahili weekly report
GET http://localhost:8080/api/report?lang=sw

### Local query
POST http://localhost:8080/api/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Which items are low in stock?"
}

### Safety route
POST http://localhost:8080/api/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Mgonjwa ana homa. Nimpe dawa gani?"
}
